author: Al Jazeera
title: China's Wuhan revises coronavirus death toll up by 50 percent
description: City where outbreak first started says 1,290 more people died of COVID-19 in sudden revision to numbers.
content:
Wuhan, the central Chinese city where the coronavirus first emerged late last year, has revised sharply upwards its death toll from the disease, admitting cases were "mistakenly reported" or missed entirely.
